OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry start in the east with
OL,6,Fsome brightness. Cloud and outbreaks
OL,7,Fof rain soon spread east, turning
OL,8,Fheavy for a time. Occasionally breezy
OL,9,Fwinds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FLargely cloudy through the
OL,12,Fevening and overnight with outbreaks
OL,13,Fof rain, occasionally heavy at first.
OL,14,FSome drier and clearer spells may
OL,15,Fdevelop at times overnight, mainly in
OL,16,Fthe west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
