OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FAny cloud and rain at first
OL,6,Fwill soon clear to bright or sunny
OL,7,Fspells in the morning. Bright spells
OL,8,Fand a few showers in the afternoon,
OL,9,Fheavy at times.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FBright
OL,12,For sunny spells and scattered showers
OL,13,FTuesday and Wednesday, some heavy and
OL,14,Fthundery. Dry, bright start on
OL,15,FThursday, cloud and rain spreading
OL,16,Feast later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
